# Source One Financial — Project Review

> **Purpose**: Dealer Performance Analytics platform for tracking activity metrics across a national dealer network.
> **Client**: Source One Financial
> **Status**: ✅ Production — deployed on Vercel, API healthy

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph External
        CSV["Daily CSV Report"]
    end

    subgraph Vercel["Vercel (Serverless)"]
        subgraph Server["Express API"]
            WH["POST /webhook"]
            AUTH["POST /auth/*"]
            ANALYTICS["GET /analytics/*"]
            REPORTS["POST /reports/*"]
        end
    end

    subgraph Pipeline["Ingestion Pipeline"]
        PARSE["CSV Parser"]
        GROUP["Dealer Group Detector"]
        INGEST["Metrics Ingestion"]
        ROLLUP["Rollup Service"]
        DIGEST["Auto Email Reports"]
    end

    subgraph MongoDB["MongoDB Atlas"]
        SNAP["DailyDealerSnapshot"]
        DG["DealerGroup"]
        DL["DealerLocation"]
        ROLL["MonthlyDealerRollup"]
        USER["User"]
    end

    subgraph Frontend["Vite + React (TypeScript)"]
        LOGIN["Login Page"]
        DASH["Dashboard"]
        FILTER["FilterBar"]
        TABLE["DealerTable"]
        SETTINGS["Settings Panel"]
        DIG_PANEL["Digest Panel"]
    end

    CSV --> WH --> PARSE --> GROUP --> INGEST --> SNAP
    INGEST --> ROLLUP --> ROLL
    INGEST --> DIGEST
    GROUP --> DG
    GROUP --> DL
    LOGIN --> AUTH
    DASH --> ANALYTICS
    SETTINGS --> REPORTS
```

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Stack | Details |
|-------|-------|---------|
| **Frontend** | Vite + React 18 (TypeScript) | CSS Modules, React Router |
| **Backend** | Node.js + Express 5 | JWT auth, role-based access |
| **Database** | MongoDB (Mongoose 9) | Atlas cloud, lazy serverless connection |
| **Deployment** | Vercel | Separate projects for client + server |
| **Email** | Nodemailer (Gmail SMTP) | Invite emails + automated digests |

---

## Key Features

### 1. 📥 Automated Data Pipeline
- **Webhook receiver** (`POST /webhook`) accepts daily CSV reports
- **CSV Parser** validates headers and extracts rows
- **Dealer Group Detector** resolves dealer names → groups + locations (with alias mapping to prevent duplicates)
- **Metrics Ingestion** bulk upserts `DailyDealerSnapshot` docs (idempotent)
- **Rollup Service** rebuilds monthly aggregates for affected months
- Entire pipeline is idempotent — safe to re-run

### 2. 📊 Analytics Dashboard
- **Three tabs**: Dealer Groups, Independent Dealers, All Dealers
- **Expandable group rows** with best/worst metrics per group
- **Multi-column sorting** with per-column removal
- **Infinite scroll** with server-side pagination
- **Server-side search** (debounced regex)
- **Status filters**: Active, 30d Inactive, 60d Inactive, Long Inactive
- **Activity mode toggle**: Track by Application, Approval, or Booking dates
- **Rep & State filtering** with budget display
- **Heatmap-colored metric cells** for visual analytics
- **Skeleton shimmer** loading states

### 3. 🔐 Invite-Only Authentication
- No public registration — admins invite users via email
- JWT-based (90-day expiry) with role hierarchy: `employee → admin → super_admin`
- Protected routes: `/analytics`, `/reports`
- Open routes: `/webhook`, `/auth`

### 4. 📧 Automated Reports
- **Daily Activity Digest**: network status breakdown, new apps/approvals/bookings, at-risk dealers, active rate progress bar
- **System Health Monitor**: alerts on row count anomalies, processing spikes, new dealer spikes, date gaps
- **Admin-configurable recipients** via Settings panel
- **Dark-themed HTML** emails matching dashboard aesthetic

### 5. ⚙️ Settings & Admin
- Profile management, password changes
- Invite new users
- Manage team (view/remove users with double-confirmation)
- Report recipients management

---

## Data Model Summary

| Model | Purpose | Key Fields |
|-------|---------|------------|
| `DealerGroup` | Multi-location brand | name, slug, dealerCount |
| `DealerLocation` | Physical dealer site | dealerId, dealerName, statePrefix, dealerGroup ref |
| `DailyDealerSnapshot` | Core metrics per dealer/day | daysSince*, activityStatus, dates |
| `MonthlyDealerRollup` | Monthly aggregations | daysActive/Inactive, avg metrics |
| `LargeDealerBudget` | Budget by state/rep | monthlyBudgets map |
| `FileIngestionLog` | CSV processing audit trail | status, rowCount, processingTimeMs |
| `WebhookPayload` | Raw webhook storage | body, files, headers |
| `User` | Auth users | email, role, status, inviteToken |
| `ReportRecipient` | Email recipients for reports | email address |

