## Presentation Talking Points

1. **End-to-end automation**: CSV → webhook → parsed → grouped → stored → rolled up → emailed — all hands-free
2. **Smart dealer grouping**: Automatic brand detection with alias mapping to prevent duplicates (Blue Compass RV with 77+ stores)
3. **Three analysis modes**: Track dealer health by Application, Approval, or Booking activity
4. **Real-time status monitoring**: Active / 30-day / 60-day / Long Inactive classification with multi-level filtering
5. **Invite-only security**: No public registration — RBAC with employee → admin → super_admin
6. **Zero-noise alerts**: Health monitor only emails when anomalies detected — no spam
7. **Serverless deployment**: Both client and server on Vercel — auto-scaling, zero ops
8. **Clean architecture**: Feature-sliced frontend, service-layer backend, comprehensive SPECS docs throughout

---

## What's NOT Built Yet (Potential Roadmap)

- No historical trend charts / time-series visualizations
- No dealer detail view / individual dealer profile page
- No export functionality (PDF reports, CSV downloads)
- No webhook retry / replay mechanism (raw payloads stored but no UI)
- No multi-tenant support (single organization)
- Report email templates are server-rendered HTML — no template editor
